1
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,880
He fell asleep.

3
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,040
I'm going to go now.

4
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,880
I've been holding back all day.

5
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:17,560
Can you take the passenger seat?

6
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,440
Jiaxu isn't your driver.

7
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,600
So? I've been your driver so many times.

8
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,760
Can't he be one for me once?

9
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,120
Bye.

10
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,000
Okay, fine!

11
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,440
Wait! My seat belt is still on!

12
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,120
You…

13
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,200
What's wrong with you?

14
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,240
I'll move.

15
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,560
Text me when you reach your dorm.

16
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,800
-"Text me."
-Bye.

17
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,800
"Bye."

18
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,760
I'm off.

19
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,800
I'll drive you home first.

20
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,320
I need to head back to the office.

21
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,960
Do you still have to work?

22
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,680
It's so late now.

23
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,520
I know.

24
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,600
I had to accompany my darling brother,

25
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,200
so I have to catch up on work tonight.

26
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,960
It's fine. I'll go with you.

27
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,680
I'm curious about how you work at night.

28
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,520
Sure.

29
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,760
Thank you, darling brother.

30
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,280
Cut it out.

31
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,160
THE DREAM GAMES

32
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,560
Why did you have to squeeze in here

33
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,880
instead of enjoying the bed at home?

34
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,400
It's all the same.

35
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,760
I'm just gaming at a different place.

36
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,360
I have a question.

37
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,600
Are you working overtime

38
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,760
on top of picking up the little demon

39
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,400
from work,

40
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,399
having dinner, going shopping,

41
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,120
and watching a movie with her?

42
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:23,320
A while ago, my superior fell sick,

43
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,360
so I was quite busy.

44
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,480
But things are better now.

45
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,360
Today is an exception.

46
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,440
Don't ruin your health just to date.

47
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,560
Actually, you can tell her.

48
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:36,800
The little demon isn't sensible,

49
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,640
but she will understand.

50
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,040
If she was sensible enough,

51
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,560
I would do whatever she wishes.

52
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,600
It's fine.

53
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,480
I'm moving to a new place soon.

54
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,720
The situation will improve.

55
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,280
New place?

56
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,160
Why are you moving?

57
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:56,080
My current place is too small

58
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,160
and far away from her campus.

59
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,960
I found a new apartment

60
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,480
with two bedrooms

61
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,720
and it's near her campus.

62
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,400
You won't have to be so worried.

63
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,360
As if.

64
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,560
Duan Jiaxu, you know me.

65
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,800
As her brother,

66
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,840
I'll worry since my sister is dating.

67
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,720
Do you remember the mess

68
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,120
when she went to see that guy

69
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,280
she met online?

70
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,920
But in the past few days,

71
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,480
I have felt relieved

72
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,600
that you are her boyfriend.

73
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,720
But mark my words.

74
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:56,040
If you ever dare to hurt my sister,

75
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,680
I will make sure you pay for it.

76
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,160
It's a shame

77
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,400
that you won't have this chance.

78
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,640
So about working late tonight…

79
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,320
No worries. I won't tell her.

80
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,400
I'm not that clueless.

81
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,720
Continue with your work.

82
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,800
Thank you, darling brother.

83
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,200
CHAPTER 21, RELIANCE

84
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,760
I AM BECAUSE YOU ARE

85
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,520
Hello. Good morning.

86
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,680
Did he sleep here again?

87
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,760
He worked overtime.

88
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,280
Again?

89
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:11,280
I'M GOING BACK TO YOUR PLACE FIRST

90
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,040
Jiaxu, good morning.

91
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,960
Good morning.

92
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,600
Did you stay here again yesterday?

93
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,600
I saw your girlfriend at the KTV

94
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,080
a few days ago.

95
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,800
-Really?
-Yes.

96
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,080
I saw her in the corridor

97
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,920
with the girl who made a scene downstairs.

98
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,240
They were talking.

99
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,560
Jiaxu, I'll get back to my work.

100
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,320
Go ahead.

101
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,680
If anything falls off,
come back to see me.

102
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,880
-I'll fix it for free.
-Sure.

103
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:07,200
-I'll get going. Bye.
-Bye.

104
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,080
Duan Jiaxu?

105
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,280
What brings you here?

106
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,120
Would you like anything to drink? Water?

107
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,800
What you did to me constitutes harassment.

108
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,400
If you go to her again,

109
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,800
I'll consider calling the police.

110
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,919
Police?

111
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,320
Jiang Ying.

112
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,840
You've been bugging me for many years

113
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,000
and I've let it go.

114
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,640
I can tolerate it all.

115
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,160
But if you hurt her,

116
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,280
the girl I love,

117
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:01,200
I can do anything for her sake.

118
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,680
PUBLIC SECURITY
ADMINISTRATIVE PUNISHMENTS LAW

119
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,960
According to our statistics,

120
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,720
the users of Dongjie

121
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,480
prioritize ingredients and additives

122
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:30,120
when choosing skincare products.

123
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,800
So we would like to showcase

124
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:35,400
the production of the main ingredients
and extraction process

125
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,640
in the animation.

126
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,960
This will give the audience a clearer view

127
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,200
of the product's safety.

128
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:46,920
Any thoughts on this?

129
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,560
The target audience of this product

130
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,640
are individuals
with allergic skin conditions

131
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,480
and individuals with sensitive skin.

132
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:57,560
I believe the users will be concerned
about the safety of the ingredients.

133
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,600
I think

134
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,920
Xiaoyu's idea is quite good.

135
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,120
I don't care what you think,

136
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,240
I only care what I think.

137
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,240
I think your opinion isn't accurate.

138
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,200
What do you think?

139
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:09,040
What the users are concerned about

140
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,880
are not necessarily our clients' concerns.

141
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,280
They value nothing but sales.

142
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,120
Mr. Zhang.

143
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,520
Dongjie's products are high-priced.

144
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,760
Their user base mainly consists of people

145
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,280
between 26 and 36.

146
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:23,000
Ladies within this age range
don't mind spending money.

147
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,200
Instead, they're concerned

148
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:26,080
about getting unsafe products
for their money.

149
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,720
That's why we went in this direction.

150
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:30,320
Dongjie is a well-established brand

151
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,080
in the market.

152
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,240
Do you think it's meaningful

153
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,200
when you advertise the ingredients?

154
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,720
I want bold and creative ideas.

155
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:41,400
Only by doing so can we help our clients

156
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,760
attract new customers.

157
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,680
This idea is indeed not persuasive enough.

158
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:49,200
Let's hear Xiaoyu's other ideas.

159
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,560
-Mr. Zhang--
-Enough.

160
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,680
You can save it.

161
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,400
Does anyone else have ideas?

162
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,360
You?

163
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,600
The two of you?

164
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,480
I have a tiny idea.

165
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,480
Go on.

166
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,400
Can we

167
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:15,200
portray the products
as animated characters?

168
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,680
Previously,

169
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,640
the client mentioned three focal points.

170
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,720
One, storytelling.

171
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,360
Two, product functionality.

172
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:29,120
Three, garnering public attention.

173
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,680
So can we use

174
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,960
an animated character

175
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:36,160
combined with the product

176
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:38,640
to create a story in the ad

177
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,960
to highlight the function of the product?

178
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,440
We can also make use

179
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,640
of some current hot topics

180
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:47,800
to generate more public interest
in the product

181
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:50,240
and reach out to a wider audience.

182
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,760
Are you positive

183
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:54,560
that using a story plot

184
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:57,320
can help raise Dongjie's sales?

185
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,280
Yes, as someone

186
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:07,000
who has had allergies since I was little.

187
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:09,600
So if I were to see this ad,

188
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:12,840
it might evoke some childhood memories.

189
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:15,240
Perhaps we can narrow the scope

190
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,800
to the allergic cluster.

191
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:19,000
If anyone with allergies watches this ad,

192
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:21,720
they may want to try the product.

193
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,480
That's an interesting idea.

194
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,440
Go into detail.

195
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,480
Detail?

196
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,960
-Details.
-I haven't thought about the details yet.

197
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,200
I think

198
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:37,640
the story of a little girl

199
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,680
doesn't align with the image
of Dongjie's product.

200
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:42,080
It's a bit too childish.

201
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:45,280
But I think it's pretty good.

202
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,400
It's interesting.

203
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:47,920
For both of your ideas,

204
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,400
one is about function,

205
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,080
while the other one is about creativity.

206
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:53,680
Anyway, the client has the final say.

207
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:57,280
I suggest making proposals for both

208
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,520
and letting the client choose.

209
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,120
I agree with Mr. Zhang.

210
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,320
I agree with your agreement.

211
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,360
So let's proceed this way.

212
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:07,200
Dongjie is our biggest client.

213
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,160
We must not lose this client,

214
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:12,080
so we must make sure to satisfy Dongjie.

215
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,240
Understood?

216
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,160
Understood.

217
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,920
Very good.

218
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,160
Young lady,

219
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,120
your idea is creative and bold.

220
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,360
Okay, let's call it a day.

221
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,600
Are you a Yihe University student?

222
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,320
A freshman.

223
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,320
Keep up the good work.

224
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,400
Sang Zhi, come here.

225
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,160
I'll send you the project material.

226
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,800
-Go back and study it.
-Sure.

227
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:45,960
Xiaoyu,

228
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:47,720
I need you to review a project.

229
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,360
Make this part bigger.

230
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,480
Okay, next page.

231
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,240
This part is quite good.

232
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,200
Xiaoyu.

233
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,240
Sang Zhi.

234
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:15,920
Xiaoyu.

235
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:18,000
I'll submit the proposal to you

236
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,240
after I complete it.

237
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,320
No need to send it to me.

238
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,240
You're an intern.

239
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:30,040
Do you not know the company rules?

240
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,560
You're my subordinate.

241
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,280
You should've reported to me

242
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,520
if you have ideas or proposals

243
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:40,240
instead of mentioning them in the meeting.

244
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,600
What was your intent?

245
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,920
What do you want?

246
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,160
To show off that you're smart?

247
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,080
No.

248
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,640
I'm sorry, Xiaoyu.

249
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,720
I just…

250
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,280
But I should've expected it.

251
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:57,240
Someone who steals
someone else's boyfriend

252
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,080
wouldn't care about the rules.

253
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:19,560
It's blazing hot in Yihe.

254
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,520
Have you been waiting long?

255
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,520
Not really.

256
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,400
Where is Duan Jiaxu?

257
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:29,640
He went to buy a drink for you.

258
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:34,760
I heard

259
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,680
that you always work extra hours.

260
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:39,800
It happens to all interns.

261
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:43,840
Well, while you're working,

262
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,640
take care of yourself and get enough rest.

263
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,480
I'm flying back tomorrow morning

264
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,880
and I have something to do later,

265
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,800
so I'm leaving now.

266
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,720
Flying back tomorrow morning?

267
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:03,480
What's wrong with you?

268
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,360
You're leaving after only a few days.

269
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,360
I need to go back
to deal with a lot of things.

270
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,600
You should've told me earlier.

271
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:11,840
I could've taken yesterday off

272
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,280
to show you around Yihe.

273
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:16,360
No, I wouldn't like your idea of fun,
little demon.

274
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,280
Forget it.

275
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,440
Well…

276
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,440
Can't you stay here

277
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,520
for two more days?

278
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,800
I…

279
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:26,760
What?

280
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,240
I…

281
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:35,320
Don't you feel embarrassed crying

282
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:36,680
outside your workplace?

283
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,120
Well…

284
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,760
I have nothing to do here.

285
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:44,000
I'm just sitting on his couch every day

286
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,840
like his watchdog.

287
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,080
I mean it.

288
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:51,280
Hey.

289
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:54,880
Something is wrong with you.

290
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,400
Are you unhappy with your internship?

291
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,480
I knew it. Here's the thing.

292
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,440
Listen.

293
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:05,040
If you're not happy, just quit the job.

294
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:07,440
We have enough money
to feed ourselves, right?

295
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:10,240
I give you more than that chump change.

296
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:13,240
How about this? I'll talk to your boss.

297
00:17:13,319 --> 00:17:15,119
I won't allow anyone to bully my sister.

298
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,280
-Got it?
-What happened?

299
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:18,240
Duan Jiaxu, come quickly.

300
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,280
Come and cheer her up.

301
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:20,440
What's going on?

302
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:22,200
-Comfort her.
-Stop bullying your sister.

303
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:24,119
It's not me. She said it's her internship.

304
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,200
-She's unhappy.
-I didn't.

305
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:27,680
He's talking nonsense.

306
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,760
You blocked me

307
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:31,000
and stole my red packets.

308
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,320
That's why I'm upset.

309
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,960
I was just messing with you.

310
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,440
I'll give you back the red packets.

311
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,960
Fine. Stop talking.

312
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,760
Here. Drink this.

313
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,680
Duan Jiaxu, I have plans later.

314
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,720
Send her home first.

315
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,080
I can give you a ride.

316
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,160
No, it's too much trouble.

317
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,480
It's in the opposite direction.

318
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:56,960
All right. You guys talk. I'm off.

319
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,960
You've got Duan Jiaxu. Aren't you happy?

320
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,440
Bye, little demon.

321
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,400
Is your boss on the second floor?

322
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,640
No…

323
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,640
-What?
-Let's go.

324
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,560
Let's go.

325
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,680
Have you been

326
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:34,520
in a bad mood lately?

327
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:39,120
I thought you hadn't talked about work

328
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:41,280
because you weren't having trouble.

329
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:48,440
There aren't that many troubles at work.

330
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:49,920
I…

331
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,840
I feel that I can handle it myself.

332
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:55,400
You're busy with your work.

333
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:59,040
I don't want to give you more pressure.

334
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:03,560
You used to cry a lot in front of me.

335
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:05,640
Why do you feel embarrassed now?

336
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,600
That was when I was a kid.

337
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:10,560
I don't cry anymore.

338
00:19:11,080 --> 00:19:11,920
Only…

339
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,440
Only kids cry.

340
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:16,480
I'm an adult now.

341
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:18,000
When I face any problems,

342
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:20,680
I should think about how to resolve them.

343
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:22,200
I can't cry all the time.

344
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:25,160
If you think

345
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,680
that only kids get to cry,

346
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:29,320
then you can always be a kid.

347
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:32,440
I'll provide for you.

348
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:38,880
All right?

349
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,800
Are you homesick?

350
00:19:58,600 --> 00:19:59,520
Let's go home then.

351
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,600
I'll take some days off

352
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:03,680
and go home with you.

353
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,760
And you can quit this job

354
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:08,600
if you don't feel like continuing it.

355
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,400
What's wrong with this company?

356
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:13,240
They keep giving my Zhizhi a hard time.

357
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,160
I must have

358
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:19,320
a serious talk with your superior.

359
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,160
Honestly.

360
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,040
You're acting like a parent now.

361
00:20:25,840 --> 00:20:27,000
Yes.

362
00:20:27,080 --> 00:20:29,240
Perhaps I've become more greedy.

363
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:31,240
I want

364
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:32,920
to be more than just your boyfriend.

365
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,560
I also want to be someone you can rely on.

366
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,520
May I?

367
00:21:02,120 --> 00:21:03,040
I also want

368
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:04,560
to be someone you rely on.

369
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,840
You can

370
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:12,240
share your joys and sorrows with me.

371
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:17,640
All right.

372
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:21,840
Then we'll rely on each other.

373
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:28,520
So now can you tell me

374
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:30,360
what happened at work?

375
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,200
Zhizhi.

376
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,800
I know that Jiang Ying went to see you.

377
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,760
Don't worry.

378
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,800
I went to her

379
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,000
and warned her today.

380
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:00,920
She won't harass you anymore.

381
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:08,720
Zhizhi.

382
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:13,120
You didn't tell me

383
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:16,320
that you're having trouble at work

384
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,800
and that Jiang Ying came to you.

385
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,880
You don't have
to take on everything alone.

386
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:24,720
Promise me.

387
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,280
You'll tell me first thing

388
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:30,120
when you run into problems, okay?

389
00:22:35,040 --> 00:22:36,280
I will let you know.

390
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:40,160
I didn't tell you about Jiang Ying

391
00:22:41,520 --> 00:22:42,920
because I've grown up

392
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,200
and I can handle it.

393
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,560
You don't have to worry about me.

394
00:22:47,600 --> 00:22:49,760
I won't let her pick on me
without doing anything.

395
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,800
I can protect myself.

396
00:22:54,520 --> 00:22:55,920
I can protect you too.

397
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:12,280
What's the matter?

398
00:23:15,080 --> 00:23:16,000
I feel

399
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,560
that my Zhizhi really has grown up.

400
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:05,040
SILLY DOG TRANSFERRED 1,000 YUAN

401
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:14,880
VOICE CALL

402
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,800
SILLY DOG

403
00:24:22,320 --> 00:24:23,680
-Hello?
-Hello.

404
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:26,240
Have you received
your pocket money and allowance?

405
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:30,360
What time is your flight?

406
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:31,280
I'll see you off.

407
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:34,120
Don't act like you care about me.

408
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:35,120
Accept the money.

409
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,200
You're scaring me.

410
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,560
Well,

411
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,400
when will you come to visit me again?

412
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:42,520
When I have spare time.

413
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,520
Don't skip meals

414
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:45,920
and rest if you feel tired.

415
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,520
Also, don't throw tantrums at Duan Jiaxu

416
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:50,680
all the time.

417
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:53,480
-I never do that.
-Fine.

418
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:56,080
-I--
-Okay. I'm hanging up. Bye.

419
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:09,000
I want

420
00:25:09,080 --> 00:25:10,560
to be more than just your boyfriend.

421
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:14,720
I also want to be someone you can rely on.

422
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,480
I didn't tell you about Jiang Ying

423
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:21,040
because I've grown up

424
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,280
and I can handle it.

425
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:24,680
You don't have to worry about me.

426
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:28,080
I won't let her pick on me
without doing anything.

427
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,720
I can protect myself.

428
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:34,120
I can protect you too.

429
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:36,680
I feel

430
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:40,440
that my Zhizhi really has grown up.

431
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:54,560
That concludes the product budget summary.

432
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,160
Next, let's have our team member

433
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:57,840
propose the idea for the ad.

434
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,720
The idea for this ad

435
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,720
uses a little girl's perspective.

436
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:08,040
This little girl has suffered

437
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,880
from allergies since childhood,

438
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:12,040
so she can't eat or drink

439
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,280
what she wants.

440
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:15,720
She starts using our skincare product

441
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:18,600
and is protected by a little spirit.

442
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,040
This little spirit

443
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,880
is a symbol of the Dongjie lotion.

444
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:25,000
This ad will be about 30 seconds long.

445
00:26:25,080 --> 00:26:26,880
The plot revolves

446
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:29,640
around the little girl and Dongjie lotion.

447
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:33,000
We'll build a character image
for the users,

448
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:34,680
so that the image of a little girl

449
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:36,240
can always remind them of Dongjie.

450
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:38,240
Aside from that,

451
00:26:38,320 --> 00:26:40,000
we can build a brand image

452
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:41,760
to portray the traits of the brand,

453
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:44,360
which are pure, gorgeous, and reassuring.

454
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:46,120
Lastly, we can highlight

455
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,600
that Dongjie is a natural product.

456
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,560
That's the gist of it.

457
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:52,440
We'll proceed with the details afterward.

458
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:57,560
I like the story of the allergic girl.

459
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:03,000
But I think the production fee

460
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,760
might exceed our budget.

461
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,840
We offer you a fair price.

462
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:10,240
The difficulty comes
with the character design

463
00:27:10,320 --> 00:27:12,080
and the shooting.

464
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:14,160
Anyway, I believe
that the more challenging it is,

465
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:16,160
the more we must try it.

466
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,360
Also, I'm confident

467
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,960
that we can provide you

468
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:21,480
with a perfect outcome.

469
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,400
All right.

470
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:25,560
We've decided

471
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,200
to use the story of the little girl.

472
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:29,120
Sir, what about the contract?

473
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:31,760
Make amendments to the contract.

474
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:32,880
Sign it quickly.

475
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,280
This will be

476
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:37,120
a perfect collaboration.

477
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,520
Thank you.

478
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:39,440
Let's go.

479
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:41,520
-Xiaoyu, see them off.
-See them off.

480
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:43,080
-This way, please.
-Okay. Be careful.

481
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:52,960
Sang Zhi.

482
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,480
You're so smart.

483
00:27:57,560 --> 00:27:58,920
You have an amazing brain.

484
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,240
You're sharp as a blade,
coming up with this brilliant idea

485
00:28:01,320 --> 00:28:02,880
and securing this project.

486
00:28:03,360 --> 00:28:04,320
Do you know what this is?

487
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:08,040
You've done an excellent job, rookie.

488
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:10,240
If you pull your weight

489
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:12,320
and do well on this proposal,

490
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:15,240
I'll give the entire team a bonus!

491
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:17,680
Thank you, Mr. Zhang!

492
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:18,800
Brilliant, Mr. Zhang!

493
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,200
I've never seen you all

494
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:21,720
with such happy faces.

495
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:22,840
You're so money-obsessed.

496
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,760
Do your work well!

497
00:28:23,840 --> 00:28:24,840
-Okay!
-You've got this!

498
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,480
-Thank you, Mr. Zhang!
-Thank you, Mr. Zhang!

499
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:29,200
Sang Zhi, this is thanks to you.

500
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:30,240
No problem.

501
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:31,880
Xiaowan,

502
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:33,840
your internship is about to be over.

503
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,840
I'll treat you two to a meal this weekend.

504
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:38,360
-Sure!
-I can't make it this weekend.

505
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,760
I have plans.

506
00:28:39,840 --> 00:28:40,680
Do you?

507
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:42,080
Is it a date?

508
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:44,120
Why are you so nosy?

509
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,400
I'm inside now.

510
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,400
Where are you?

511
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:02,840
I'm going to…

512
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:10,440
Have you arrived?

513
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:16,400
What are you doing there?

514
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:27,040
Wait for me there. I'll come to get you.

515
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:31,120
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

516
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,120
Will it be…

517
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:42,120
Change into slippers first.

518
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,560
Take a look around first.

519
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,280
There's a kitchen over here.

520
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:04,920
There are two bedrooms.

521
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,680
This room has a bigger balcony.

522
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,200
It's your room.

523
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,280
Does this mean

524
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:19,160
that we are living together?

525
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:21,680
No.

526
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:24,080
I thought of giving you a place to rest

527
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,920
when you get tired from studying.

528
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,320
Let's go eat.

529
00:30:36,080 --> 00:30:36,920
By the way,

530
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:40,200
you haven't told me

531
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:43,120
how much the monthly rent is.

532
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,360
Is it expensive?

533
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,720
If it's expensive,

534
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,360
you don't have to rent this place.

535
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,920
Are you afraid that I can't afford it?

536
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:54,000
No.

537
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,400
I'm afraid

538
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,520
that you are wasting money.

539
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,480
I can afford this.

540
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:03,240
I'm renting this place

541
00:31:03,320 --> 00:31:04,480
because it's near your campus.

542
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:06,640
You can have more time to rest.

543
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:12,800
Give me your hand.

544
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,800
Why?

545
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,160
From now on,

546
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,640
this is our home.

547
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,480
Hello, ma'am.

548
00:32:27,560 --> 00:32:29,600
This is room 202.

549
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:31,840
I think something is wrong
with the air conditioner.

550
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,840
What can I do?

551
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,200
It's summer break

552
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,640
and the technician isn't on duty.

553
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:36,720
No one can fix it.

554
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,560
You'll have to wait until next semester.

555
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:42,240
Can I hire a technician myself?

556
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:43,880
I don't recommend that.

557
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:46,560
If the fix makes it worse,
you'll have to pay for it.

558
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:48,080
But the room is really hot.

559
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:51,360
You'll have to find another solution.

560
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,520
All right. Bye.

561
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,440
Hello, Jiaxu.

562
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,520
What are you doing, kiddo?

563
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:17,480
Have you had dinner?

564
00:33:17,560 --> 00:33:18,720
I've eaten.

565
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:20,440
But the air conditioner
in my dorm isn't working.

566
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:21,640
The room is stifling.

567
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:28,040
I see.

568
00:33:30,560 --> 00:33:31,640
I'll go and fetch you now.

569
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,200
Fetch me to go where?

570
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,360
My place.

571
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:43,560
Wait for me on campus.

572
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,880
I'll be on my way now.

573
00:33:47,280 --> 00:33:48,160
All right.

574
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,640
It's so refreshing.

575
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,680
Here.

576
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,880
It must be hot in your room.

577
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:08,760
Change your shoes.

578
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:16,560
Take a look.

579
00:34:17,040 --> 00:34:18,360
See what you want to eat.

580
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:22,960
I bought all your favorite snacks for you.

581
00:34:27,159 --> 00:34:31,040
Today, I'll have this

582
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:33,000
and…

583
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,840
This.

584
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:38,040
Do you want to try this?

585
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:45,239
I'm all good with these.

586
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:47,239
I'll eat the rest tomorrow.

587
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:48,679
Okay.

588
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,280
Have a taste.

589
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:57,640
You go first.

590
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:58,600
Don't you want it?

591
00:34:58,680 --> 00:34:59,960
You take the first bite.

592
00:35:04,160 --> 00:35:05,080
Is it good?

593
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,760
You can have these every day

594
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,120
if you move in.

595
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,680
I'll go and tidy up the place.

596
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:30,320
Do you want to take a shower?

597
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,880
I've prepared the toiletries for you
in the bathroom.

598
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,800
Weren't you sweating in your dorm?

599
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,800
Go ahead and wash up.

600
00:35:47,680 --> 00:35:49,680
All right. I'll go now.

601
00:36:11,720 --> 00:36:12,800
Are you done?

602
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:15,760
Why did he change into pajamas?

603
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,960
Why are you standing there?

604
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:23,440
I'm working.

605
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:28,920
I'm playing a game.

606
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:33,240
Is it the same game as before?

607
00:36:34,680 --> 00:36:35,800
Come and play with me.

608
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:45,040
Have you tried this before?

609
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,600
Let me show you.

610
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,760
The first skill.

611
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,440
Shoot. Shoot outward.

612
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:02,800
The second skill is range.

613
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,560
I'm teaching you how to play.

614
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,200
Give it a try.

615
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:16,360
Here.

616
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:23,120
Buy the equipment.

617
00:37:25,560 --> 00:37:26,800
Attack them with the skills.

618
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:39,520
Focus on the game.

619
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,480
What should I do now?

620
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:55,760
Run.

621
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:57,400
Run.

622
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,280
It's fine. You did very well.

623
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,800
I'll go get some snacks.

624
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:08,040
You…

625
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:09,560
Let me see.

626
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:14,640
Take your time.

627
00:38:14,720 --> 00:38:15,560
I…

628
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:19,360
Can I unbutton it?

629
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:11,680
It's done.

630
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,560
You have

631
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:14,960
to work tomorrow, right?

632
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:19,200
Maybe you should go to bed now.

633
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,200
Yes.

634
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:27,760
I am a bit sleepy.

635
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:30,040
I think I had better rest now.

636
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,560
I need to go to work early.

637
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,680
I still have some work to do.

638
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:45,920
Remember to lock your door.

639
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:14,240
Good morning.

640
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:15,360
Good morning.

641
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,040
I'll make breakfast for you.

642
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:26,480
I'll help you.

643
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,440
Try it.

644
00:42:51,240 --> 00:42:52,520
By the way,

645
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:54,640
are you getting off work late today?

646
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:56,480
Tell me before you leave.

647
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:57,680
I'll pick you up.

648
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,400
There's no need.

649
00:43:00,080 --> 00:43:01,760
I can come back myself.

650
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:05,600
Also, isn't your game
going into the testing phase soon?

651
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:07,800
My internship is ending soon.

652
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:09,000
After that,

653
00:43:09,080 --> 00:43:11,920
we can have more free time to hang out.

654
00:43:12,880 --> 00:43:13,840
All right.

655
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:16,760
When the testing phase is over,

656
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:18,720
we can go anywhere you want.
